title: Spacious Floor Plans, Private Entry, Swimming Pool with Picnic Area
posting_body: ['Huntington House’s plush, landscaped courtyards with two community pools, walking paths, sundecks, barbecues and picnic tables welcomes residents with the perfect environment to call “home”.', 'Each apartment offers spacious floor plans, beautiful views of the courtyards and private entry.', 'Located on Fort Street enjoy Huntington House’s neighborhood charm in the city.', 'We would love for you to come on by and see what Huntington House has to offer!', '-Package Acceptance', '-Sparkling Clean Swimming Pool', '-No Security Deposit Required', '-Upgraded Units Available', '-Private Entrance', '-Air Conditioned', '-One $35 Application Fee Per Apartment, Not Per Person', '-Picture Windows with Courtyard Views', '-BBQ & Picnic Area', '-Radiant Baseboard Heat', '-Additional Storage', '-Online Payment Options (Credit Card, Debit Card and ACH)', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
